- OSP ------
  Welcome Oistes!

  Logged in as  oistes
  Theme         Rose Pine Moon
  Version       1.4.9
- Keybindings 
  Ctrl-D  exit
  Ctrl-L  clear screen
  Ctrl-R  reverse search history
- Pipes ----
  F key>3                    V value-only quick search
  P col1 col2                contains quick-search text
  S sort_key                 !not negate a quick match
  G group_by_k1 k2           ?exist truthy / exists
  A metric()                 !?not_exist missing / falsy
  L limit offset             = exact exact match (ci)
  C count                    == case-sens. exact match (cs)
  K key-only quick search    | H <verb> verb help, e.g. | H F
- Usage ----
  [INVOCATION_OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...
